# Sea Creature Facts Generator

A simple, single-page web application that displays random interesting facts about sea creatures.

## Description

This project is a lightweight web application that presents users with fascinating facts about various sea creatures. It features a clean, ocean-themed interface and allows users to generate random facts about different marine animals with a single click.

## Features

- Random fact generation
- Responsive design
- Ocean-themed visual interface
- Single-file implementation
- 20 unique sea creature facts

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)

## Installation

1. Download the `index.html` file
2. Open it in any modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)

No additional installation or dependencies required!

## Usage

1. Open the application in your web browser
2. Click the "Get New Fact" button to generate a random sea creature fact
3. The fact card will display the creature name and an interesting fact about it

## Project Structure

The entire application is contained in a single `index.html` file which includes:
- HTML structure
- CSS styling (in the `<style>` tag)
- JavaScript functionality (in the `<script>` tag)
- Sea creature facts data

## Contributing

Feel free to fork this project and submit pull requests to contribute additional sea creature facts or enhance the functionality.

